\c 17
\nb
\v 1 Umoya wami wonakele, insuku zami zicitshiwe\x + 18.5,6.\x*, amangcwaba ngawami\x + Hlab. 88.3,4.\x*.
\v 2 Kabakho lami yini abaklolodayo, lelihlo lami lichitha ubusuku ekuvukeleni kwabo?
\v 3 Akubeke isibambiso sami kuwe\x + Isa. 38.14. Hlab. 119.122. Heb. 7.22.\x*; ngubani yena \add o\add*zatshaya esandleni sami\x + Zaga 6.1.\x*?
\v 4 Ngoba inhliziyo yabo uyifihlele ukuqedisisa; ngenxa yalokhu kawuyikubaphakamisa.
\v 5 Okhuluma ngokuyenga kubangane, lamehlo abantwana bakhe azafiphala\x + 11.20.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo ungimise ngaba yisaga sezizwe\x + 30.9. Hlab. 44.14. 69.11. Dute. 28.37. Jow. 2.17.\x*, ngaze ngaba ngokhafulelwayo phambi kwazo.
\v 7 Njalo ilihlo lami lifiphele ngosizi\x + Hlab. 6.7.\x*, lamalunga ami anjengesithunzi wonke\x + 14.2.\x*.
\v 8 Abaqotho bazakwethuswa yikho\x + Isa. 52.14.\x*, longelacala uvukela ongamesabiyo uNkulunkulu\x + 31.29.\x*.
\v 9 Lolungileyo uzabambelela endleleni yakhe, lolezandla ezihlambulukileyo uzakwengeza amandla\x + 22.30. Hlab. 24.4.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa-ke lina lonke, phendukani ake libuye, ngoba kangitholi ohlakaniphileyo phakathi kwenu\x + 6.29.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Insuku zami zedlule\x + 7.6. 9.25.\x*, amacebo ami adabuke phakathi\x + 18.14.\x*, \add le\add*zifiso zenhliziyo yami.
\v 12 Bamisa ubusuku bube yimini\x + Isa. 5.20.\x*; ukukhanya kuseduze\x + 7.4.\x* phambi kobumnyama\x + 23.17.\x*.
\v 13 Uba ngilinda, ingcwaba lizakuba yindlu yami\x + Tshu. 12.5.\x*; ngendlala umbheda wami emnyameni.
\v 14 Ngibiza ingcwaba ngisithi: Wena ungubaba; impethu ngisithi: Umama lodadewethu.
\v 15 Pho-ke ithemba lami lingaphi? Yebo, ithemba lami ngubani ozalibona?
\v 16 Kuzakwehlela \add ku\add*mijabo yengcwaba\x + 18.13.\x*, lapho\x + 3.17,18,19.\x* sizaphumula\x + 36.16.\x* khona ndawonye enhlabathini\x + 21.26. 40.13.\x*.
